1
00:00:18,559 --> 00:00:19,440
Chamberlain An is weak,

2
00:00:19,679 --> 00:00:21,160
and gets palpitations easily.

3
00:00:21,359 --> 00:00:22,679
After acupuncture and taking medicine,

4
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:23,359
she'll be fine.

5
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:34,439
I was reckless last night,

6
00:00:34,679 --> 00:00:35,520
trespassing the forbidden area.

7
00:00:37,079 --> 00:00:38,119
Thank you for not holding it against me,

8
00:00:39,119 --> 00:00:40,200
and for your concern.

9
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:41,520
Don't worry.

10
00:00:42,079 --> 00:00:42,880
Take care of yourself.

11
00:00:50,380 --> 00:00:50,859
Chamberlain An,

12
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:03,000
the key to the vault

13
00:01:03,320 --> 00:01:04,400
is the finger ring

14
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:06,219
that Xie Huaiyun never leaves.

15
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:07,920
Let me.

16
00:01:12,519 --> 00:01:13,599
I dare not trouble you.

17
00:01:13,900 --> 00:01:14,920
You are the chamberlain

18
00:01:14,920 --> 00:01:15,799
of the Bureau of Treasures.

19
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,159
If something goes wrong,

20
00:01:17,920 --> 00:01:18,799
I can't explain it.

21
00:01:32,719 --> 00:01:33,859
It's so bitter.

22
00:01:36,079 --> 00:01:36,840
The most effective medicine is often bitter.

23
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:52,079
Are you alright, Lady An?

24
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:54,920
I'm fine.

25
00:01:55,599 --> 00:01:56,799
I was too reckless.

26
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,040
My lord,

27
00:01:58,680 --> 00:01:59,560
is your hand okay?

28
00:02:01,359 --> 00:02:02,079
Of course.

29
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:03,480
My lord,

30
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:14,900
no need to clean up.

31
00:02:16,159 --> 00:02:16,960
Go prepare another bowl of medicine

32
00:02:17,460 --> 00:02:18,259
and get some preserved fruits.

33
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:19,199
Yes, sir.

34
00:02:34,599 --> 00:02:35,039
[Pills?]

35
00:02:41,259 --> 00:02:42,039
[Every seven days,]

36
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:44,199
[Xie Huaiyun takes the pills.]

37
00:02:44,620 --> 00:02:45,479
[That's the best time]

38
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,560
[to sneak into]

39
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,560
[the vault.]

40
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:53,639
My lord.

41
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,120
Send out the order.

42
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,900
Triple the guards at the vault.

43
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,759
Anyone who approaches without permission

44
00:03:03,479 --> 00:03:04,560
will be killed on sight.

45
00:03:05,219 --> 00:03:05,620
Yes, sir.

46
00:03:22,639 --> 00:03:23,460
[An Rao,]

47
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:25,840
[are you a medicine]

48
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,240
[or a poison?]

49
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,580
This is a replica
of the key to the vault.

50
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,479
I'm fine.

51
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,520
I was too reckless.

52
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:50,800
My Lord,

53
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,120
is your hand okay?

54
00:03:54,879 --> 00:03:56,120
Everything goes according to plan.

55
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,319
When it's midnight,

56
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,280
you'll meet Xie Lingfeng.

57
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:04,840
It's midnight.

58
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,759
Where's the sugar bag?

59
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,240
If I can't get it,

60
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,160
I can't...

61
00:04:30,420 --> 00:04:30,899
Who's there?

62
00:04:43,079 --> 00:04:44,079
Thank you, General Jin.

63
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,439
Why are you here? Where's your sister?

64
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:49,680
I...

65
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,000
Sister, catch them.

66
00:04:52,480 --> 00:04:53,680
Don't let them go.

67
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,560
Yes.

68
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,000
I'll hold them off.
You escape when you get a chance.

69
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,120
Sister,

70
00:05:12,600 --> 00:05:13,439
I'm useless.

71
00:05:13,959 --> 00:05:15,120
I can't help you at all.

72
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:40,360
Little slave,

73
00:05:41,839 --> 00:05:42,759
Do you miss me?

74
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,180
Are you Su Luoyao

75
00:06:38,180 --> 00:06:39,000
or An Rao?

76
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:41,560
Or are you the same person?

77
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,199
Little slave.

78
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:45,480
Call me master.

79
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,680
Guess

80
00:06:58,920 --> 00:06:59,720
how many secrets

81
00:07:00,839 --> 00:07:02,480
you are hiding.

82
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:12,439
What's going on?

83
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,439
I didn't take the pill.

84
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,759
My lord,

85
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:17,600
the thief...

86
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:19,040
The thief has escaped.

87
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,439
Useless!

88
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:24,040
You're all useless!

89
00:07:26,319 --> 00:07:27,519
What good are you to me?

90
00:07:41,319 --> 00:07:42,279
Thank you, my lord.

91
00:07:51,759 --> 00:07:53,120
Lady An, what are you afraid of?

92
00:07:54,480 --> 00:07:55,480
Are you afraid of me,

93
00:07:57,079 --> 00:07:59,000
or afraid of being seen through by me?

94
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,439
Aren't you the goddess who can

95
00:08:04,439 --> 00:08:05,720
all misfortunes?

96
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:08,360
Then look at me,

97
00:08:09,040 --> 00:08:09,800
these sins,

98
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:11,959
this blood,

99
00:08:14,259 --> 00:08:15,660
can you really absolve them?

100
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,220
Let me go!

101
00:08:19,639 --> 00:08:20,279
Can you?

102
00:08:21,019 --> 00:08:21,660
Absolve me!

103
00:08:49,120 --> 00:08:49,679
I'm sorry,

104
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:50,960
I never meant to hurt you.

105
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,080
The lotus under your pen,

106
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,240
can wash away everything,

107
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,080
then wash me,

108
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:03,919
wash these dirty hands of mine,

109
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:06,960
wash this heart of mine

110
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,320
that has long rotted away.

111
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,919
The sins on my back are too heavy,

112
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:17,799
pressing down on me so much that my bones creak.

113
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:20,360
I can't breathe.

114
00:09:28,120 --> 00:09:28,759
An Rao,

115
00:09:31,639 --> 00:09:32,879
can you help me?

116
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:55,200
How did you

117
00:09:56,960 --> 00:09:57,879
get these scars?

118
00:09:59,120 --> 00:10:00,159
It was eight years ago.

119
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:04,039
The massacre.

120
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,120
I was burned by fire.

121
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:07,759
Since that day,

122
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,639
I've been afraid of fire.

123
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:13,000
These scars are the marks left behind,

124
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,279
a debt I can never repay.

125
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:19,039
Whenever I see these scars,

126
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,080
I'm reminded

127
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,000
the blood of those people

128
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:24,120
sprayed all over me.

129
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,039
It can't be washed away.

130
00:10:35,960 --> 00:10:37,320
It can never be washed away.

131
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:48,440
I'm sure you had no choice

132
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,320
at that time.

133
00:10:53,639 --> 00:10:54,240
No.

134
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,480
I had no choice.

135
00:10:58,600 --> 00:11:00,120
They didn't deserve to die.

136
00:11:00,679 --> 00:11:02,799
It should have been me.

137
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:05,960
An Rao,

138
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:09,440
If there are gods in this world,

139
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,320
will they forgive someone like me?

140
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,440
Gods don't save people.

141
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,720
People must save themselves.

142
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:18,840
If you can get out of

143
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:19,799
your own prison,

144
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,840
you can become your own god.

145
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,240
Lotus grows in the mire,

146
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,559
yet remains pure and clean.

147
00:11:37,799 --> 00:11:38,799
May this flower

148
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:40,600
shield you

149
00:11:41,080 --> 00:11:42,000
[from the past.]

150
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,039
[Lady An.]

151
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,200
[You are my lotus.]

152
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:58,919
My lord.

153
00:11:59,639 --> 00:12:00,120
My lord.

154
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,240
My lord, let go of me.

155
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,039
My lord.

156
00:12:03,639 --> 00:12:04,080
My lord.

157
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:07,120
My lord.

158
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,940
You know he's not in his right mind.

159
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:41,120
Why did you get close to him?

160
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:41,679
You...

161
00:12:44,480 --> 00:12:45,139
You're willing to

162
00:12:45,139 --> 00:12:46,200
risk your life like this?

163
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,039
I didn't realize it at the time.

164
00:12:57,279 --> 00:12:58,120
You are An Rao.

165
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:03,559
So from start to finish,

166
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:04,840
you are the same person.

167
00:13:06,879 --> 00:13:08,159
My sister and I

168
00:13:08,519 --> 00:13:10,320
have our reasons.

169
00:13:10,759 --> 00:13:12,240
We didn't mean to deceive you.

170
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:21,080
If that's the case,

171
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,039
stay away from him.

172
00:13:25,639 --> 00:13:27,399
You should know how to protect yourself.

173
00:13:33,039 --> 00:13:34,559
[Was he so angry]

174
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:36,559
[because he was worried about me,]

175
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:38,360
[or]

176
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,480
[was he worried about]

177
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:42,139
[someone else through me?]
